Titolo: Hidden & Dangerous 2

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Hidden & Dangerous 2 is a tactical shooter video game developed by Illusion Softworks and published by Gathering of Developers. It was released October 2003 for Microsoft Windows. It is the second installment and the direct sequel to 2K Czech's predecessor Hidden & Dangerous, it features similar gameplay concepts and themes. Illusion Softworks and creative director Petr Vochozka based the game's setting on stealth based British Special Air Service operations behind Axis lines during the Second World War.

Genere: Non specificato


